      "title": "Sri Lanka shares over 1-pct gain in mid-day trade",
      "author": "",
      "body_lines": [
        "ECONOMYNEXT \u2013 Sri Lanka\u2019s shares gained in mid-day trade on Tuesday (30) after slipping for 5 straight sessions, the Colombo Stock Exchange data showed.",
        "The main All Share Price index gained 1.55 percent or 135.39 points to 8,867.86 at 1145 hours.",
        "\u201cThe market moved up as the margin selling in eased and there\u2019s a speculation that an IMF deal would be signed on Wednesday,\u201d a market analyst said."
